title: Beowulf Directors cut. 2 Disc 2007 [Eng, No Subs] avi
description:
A Hero steps forth, proclaiming his fame and his name.
Beowulf! Slayer of monsters. Defender of the realm.
He will kill the voracious beast ravaging the viking land.
He will claim Gold and Kingdom as his reward.
But will his unchecked ambition ultimately demand a terrible toll of him?.

Ray Winston plays the heroic title role, and Angelina Jolie portrays the seductive mother of monsters in this epic tale set in a time of demons and dragons, warriors and temptresses.
The lusty comoraderie.
The battle with grotesque Grendal.
The fiery death duel with the dragon.
All here.
All in a revolutionary new performance capture vision from filmmaker Robert Zemeckis.
Hail Beowulf! Bravest of the brave..


Enjoy, Keima
